name: Your Destiny
Lore: 'Luke''s destiny lies with his father, Darth Vader. To become a Jedi Knight, Luke must accept this.',
Text: 'Deploy on Bring Him Before Me. When Vader is present at a battleground site, at start of your turn opponent loses 3 Force unless Luke is captured, out of play, or present at a battleground site. Also, Luke is immune to Responsibility Of Command. (Immune to Alter.)',
